[
    {
        "text": "Many Korean firms have moved their factories to China...",
        "startTime": 2688,
        "endTime": 5987,
        "slowStartTime": 4182,
        "slowEndTime": 9205
    },
    {
        "text": "...expecting to receive a large labor cost-savings.",
        "startTime": 6117,
        "endTime": 8967,
        "slowStartTime": 9326,
        "slowEndTime": 13676
    },
    {
        "text": "And some of those same Korean firms wish to achieve similar cost-savings with their factories here...",
        "startTime": 9460,
        "endTime": 14720,
        "slowStartTime": 14340,
        "slowEndTime": 22305
    },
    {
        "text": "...by bringing workers from China.",
        "startTime": 14839,
        "endTime": 16372,
        "slowStartTime": 22408,
        "slowEndTime": 24783
    },
    {
        "text": "Chinese workers believe if they go to Korea,...",
        "startTime": 17543,
        "endTime": 19741,
        "slowStartTime": 26465,
        "slowEndTime": 29836
    },
    {
        "text": "...they'll earn about 10 times more than in China.",
        "startTime": 20136,
        "endTime": 22886,
        "slowStartTime": 30354,
        "slowEndTime": 34554
    },
    {
        "text": "They also think it is best to be recruited by their own company...",
        "startTime": 23441,
        "endTime": 26593,
        "slowStartTime": 35311,
        "slowEndTime": 40114
    },
    {
        "text": "...because it costs less than other ways of coming to Korea to work.",
        "startTime": 26983,
        "endTime": 30391,
        "slowStartTime": 40625,
        "slowEndTime": 45812
    },
    {
        "text": "However, there is one big problem with this scenario.",
        "startTime": 31329,
        "endTime": 34325,
        "slowStartTime": 47143,
        "slowEndTime": 51713
    },
    {
        "text": "After arriving, they are naturally quite angry upon finding out that...",
        "startTime": 34895,
        "endTime": 38331,
        "slowStartTime": 52492,
        "slowEndTime": 57721
    },
    {
        "text": "...Korea has different pay scales for:",
        "startTime": 38442,
        "endTime": 40455,
        "slowStartTime": 57813,
        "slowEndTime": 60907
    },
    {
        "text": "One, undocumented (illegal) workers",
        "startTime": 41044,
        "endTime": 44078,
        "slowStartTime": 61716,
        "slowEndTime": 66342
    },
    {
        "text": "Two, migrant workers registered as trainees...",
        "startTime": 44529,
        "endTime": 47824,
        "slowStartTime": 66944,
        "slowEndTime": 71961
    },
    {
        "text": "...by the Korea Federation of Small and Medium Businesses",
        "startTime": 47953,
        "endTime": 50981,
        "slowStartTime": 72079,
        "slowEndTime": 76697
    },
    {
        "text": "Three, trainees from overseas invested companies.",
        "startTime": 51801,
        "endTime": 55394,
        "slowStartTime": 77852,
        "slowEndTime": 83316
    },
    {
        "text": "Workers in the last group were in the worst situation. Why?",
        "startTime": 56437,
        "endTime": 60191,
        "slowStartTime": 84805,
        "slowEndTime": 90511
    },
    {
        "text": "Workers who are paid by the original factory abroad...",
        "startTime": 60761,
        "endTime": 63574,
        "slowStartTime": 91292,
        "slowEndTime": 95586
    },
    {
        "text": "...can be paid the same wage as the workers in China.",
        "startTime": 63883,
        "endTime": 66489,
        "slowStartTime": 95974,
        "slowEndTime": 99958
    },
    {
        "text": "This allows Korean companies to use a legal loophole to truly exploit migrant labor.",
        "startTime": 67222,
        "endTime": 72349,
        "slowStartTime": 100983,
        "slowEndTime": 108748
    },
    {
        "text": "Some Korean factories employ Korean workers, normal migrant workers,...",
        "startTime": 73257,
        "endTime": 77410,
        "slowStartTime": 110036,
        "slowEndTime": 116340
    },
    {
        "text": "...and migrant workers transferred from overseas factories...",
        "startTime": 77615,
        "endTime": 80478,
        "slowStartTime": 116572,
        "slowEndTime": 120942
    },
    {
        "text": "...who perform the same job,..",
        "startTime": 80980,
        "endTime": 82433,
        "slowStartTime": 121620,
        "slowEndTime": 123875
    },
    {
        "text": "...work the same hours under the same roof all on different pay scales.",
        "startTime": 82739,
        "endTime": 86970,
        "slowStartTime": 124259,
        "slowEndTime": 130680
    }
]